  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with COPD

          -  Eligible to participate in a exercise training intervention of 8 weeks

          -  Pi,max &lt;60cmH2O or &lt;50% of the predicted normal value

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Major comorbidities preventing successful participation in an 8 week exercise training
